# Repomd Gitignore

## 🦀 Rust
/target/
**/*.rs.bk
Cargo.lock

## 🐍 Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
.venv/
venv/
ENV/
env/
.env
.pytest_cache/
.coverage
htmlcov/
*.log

## 📊 Benchmark & Reports
# Keep results and UI, ignore raw generated charts and massive docs if they are transient
# benchmark_results.json
# benchmark_ui.html
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.gif
*.svg
*.docx
*.pdf
ultra_benchmark_dashboard.html

# Allow official benchmark assets
!/benchmarks/*.png
!/benchmarks/*.docx
!/benchmarks/benchmark_results.json
!/docs/*.md

## 🌐 Web & Node
node_modules/
dist/
.next/
out/
build/
.vercel
.turbo

## 📂 IDE & OS
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

## 📝 Project Specific
*.md
!README.md
!repo.md
